data.description: New Year, New Price! Priced to sell, this Golf Course Community home is located on a quiet and friendly cul-de-sac. Luxury living at it's finest, featuring beautiful Vaulted Ceilings, Immaculate hard wood floors, gorgeous windows allowing natural light and a terrific view as it backs up to the 12th green. An Open concept floor plan to include 4 Bedrooms (4th bedroom can be utilized as an office with built-ins across one wall) 3 Full Baths, and a formal dining area. Granite countertops throughout with a Spacious kitchen and Stainless Appliances, an abundance of counter space and cabinets for storage and more! Fabulous laundry room to include a mudroom sink. Glamorous Main Suite with oversized walk in closet that shows off high ceilings, plenty of storage and tons of space, double sink vanity, stand alone shower and jetted spa tub. Enjoy  your Covered back patio, swing set that stays, new wrought iron fence and views of a pond and wildlife.  It already includes a well that allows watering and inground sprinkler system to keep your exterior beautiful.
